To build the project do the foloowing:

1.	Login to ecelinux. 
2.	Open the src folder in the terminal window.
3.	Type make
4.	The program builds and should have 3 exec files: produce_process, produce_thread, and consume
5.	To test process way, type "./produce_process <N> <B> <P> <C>"
6.	To test thread way, type "./produce_thread <N> <B> <P> <C>"
7.	The output is displayed